text: World Skate Europe - Rink Hockey,World Skate Europe - Rink Hockey formerly known as Comité Européen de Rink-Hockey, is a technical committee responsible for the governing of rink hockey (or roller hockey) in Europe. World Skate Europe is one of the 5 regions governed by World Skate. ==References== ==Other websites== *Official website Category:Roller skating organizations Rink
